🇧🇷 Ronaldinho making the extraordinary look easy.

#UCL | @ronaldinho | #ThrowbackThursday

🔴 Ole Gunnar Solskjær signed for @manchesterunited #OTD in 1996 🙌 
How far will he take them in the #UCL?
